cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG

This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on the use of LIDAR sensors in the perception stack of autonomous robots. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper discusses the accuracy of different types of depth sensors. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is another possible sub-category as the paper employs gradient-based optimization to estimate model parameters. Systems and Control (cs.SY) is a relevant sub-category as the paper discusses the measurement process and calibration of LIDAR sensors. Finally, Machine Learning (cs.LG) is a possible sub-category as the paper uses automatic differentiation to estimate model parameters.
